_detail:e=>`They push the fifty aggressively via ${e}. Set a player to hold the lane and kill the runner before they reach the fifty.`,counter_pocket_action:"Survive the break — read their lanes",counter_pocket_detail:"They have 4+ players shooting from the base. Don't run through paint — wait for a reload or quiet moment, then attack the open tape.",counter_conservative_action:"Get alive, then apply pressure",counter_conservative_detail:"They play slow. Get alive on good bunkers first, then build pressure from the angles. Don't force the break.",counter_agg_start_action:"Lanes on break — free eliminations",counter_agg_start_detail:"They send many runners. Disciplined lanes off the buzzer rack up eliminations before they reach their bunkers.",counter_attack_snake_action:"Attack snake — it's exposed",counter_attack_snake_detail:"They focus on dorito. Send an aggressive player to snake — minimal resistance.",counter_attack_dorito_action:"Attack dorito — it's exposed",counter_attack_dorito_detail:"They focus on snake. Send an aggressive player to dorito — minimal resistance.",counter_side_vuln_action:e=>`Pressure through ${e} — that's where they bleed`,counter_side_vuln_detail:"Most of their losses come from this side. Repeat the attack.",counter_center_action:"Challenge their mid player",counter_center_detail:"They dominate center. Send a mid player with good lane coverage — force them to respect it.",counter_uncovered_action:e=>`Send a runner through ${e} — nobody shoots there`,counter_uncovered_detail:"This side is consistently uncovered during obstacle play. The runner will walk through unopposed.",counter_player_action:"Eliminate their key player on the break",counter_player_detail:"Without them their results drop significantly. Focus fire at the start of the point.",counter_predictable_action:"Counter their predictable setup",counter_pred_detail_nobody:"Nobody runs to tape. Your front players can enter both sides safely — the only threat is mid lanes.",counter_pr